      ["LORE"] = "The great pit of Menem-berej was once home to the richest lodes of mithril ever unearthed in Khazad-dûm. This enormous platform was constructed to assist the dwarves in their mighty efforts to extract the precious metal. Though this mine was believed to have been sapped of most of its resources by the time Moria fell, Brogur and Bósi's dwarves vow to find some valuable remnants of the riches that were once so abundant."; 
