      ["LORE"] = "The Mordath, the Black Pits of Mordor, is a place devoid of hope. It is the foundation of Barad-dûr, an ever-deepening mine, and a pit of punishment for those that have failed the Dark Lord. Those who are cast into the Black Pits will never again behold the light of Middle-earth."; 
