      ["PROGRESS"] = "Discover Thol Shíkug, the Screaming Deep"; 
      ["LORE"] = "Thol Shíkug is a fortress of terror and death built into the very foundations of Barad-dûr. For those condemned to the Black Pits, it is known as the Screaming Deep -- for many an Orc, Man, and beast have met their ends at the hands of the Dark Lord and his most powerful servants within. What lies within this grim structure, none have ever returned to tell."; 
