      ["PROGRESS"] = "Discover Howlers' Notch"; 
      ["LORE"] = "Where once the haunting howling of Wargs filled the air around Howlers' Notch, now only the guttural growling of hill-beasts can be heard. The former Warg den houses vicious hill-beasts, manipulated and bred for war by hobgoblin beast-tamers. Cages and chains imprison the wild hill-beasts that have been captured against their will."; 
