      ["LORE"] = "From the Elf-camp of Idhobel, a few folk keep watch on the dangers that have arisen in recent days in Western Eregion. The Uruks that trouble Swanfleet seem particularly interested in the ruins of the Hall of the Swift River, located to the north, and those who camp at Idhobel lead sorties against them wherever possible."; 
