      ["LORE"] = "Wolves have lived at Howlingstones for as long as the people of Mossward can remember, but they generally do not stray too near to the outer palisade. That has changed in recent nights, however, and now the town guards have seen lupine eyes staring at them from the darkness with unsettling frequency."; 
