      ["PROGRESS"] = "Find Golodir's inscription"; 
      ["LORE"] = "It was within this high chamber that Golodir was imprisoned at Gwathrenost, only granted the briefest and most unkind of freedoms on the days he was forced to peer into the palantír at Mordirith's behest. Through all of his suffering, his love for his daughter, Lorniel, never wavered and he dreamt of the day they would at last be reunited. Alas, Mordirith knew well of Golodir's hopes and his faith in those he had left behind at Gath Forthnír...."; 
