      ["LORE"] = "The ruin of Ost Norhír stands atop the hill overlooking the river south of the Harlond, but now it is inhabited only by wildlife. When the people departed to rebuild their lives in the aftermath of the war, the beasts moved back in to make homes of their own."; 
