      ["PROGRESS"] = "Find Tingobel"; 
      ["LORE"] = "Although it was sacked by the Orcs of the White Mountains during the War of the Ring, the mining village of Tingobel has been retaken by the order of Lord Duinhir. Damages to its houses have been repaired and the mine has been restored, but the lives lost in its fall have not been forgotten to any who dwell in the Blackroot Vale."; 
