      ["PROGRESS"] = "Find Sardol"; 
      ["LORE"] = "To the south of Alagrant along the River Morthond lies Sardol, a hamlet inhabited by farmers and fishermen. Before the Heirs of Castamir erected the now-ruined blockade on the road through Tarlang's Crown, Sardol served as a minor trading post for those travelling between Morlad and Dol Amroth."; 
