      ["PROGRESS"] = "Find Eryn Asgath"; 
      ["LORE"] = "Amidst the woodlands to the south-east of the Hill of Erech near Tarlang's Neck lies Eryn Asgath, a den inhabited by the invasive wolves that have crept in from Lamedon and the surrounding hills. With their terrible howls echoing in the night, the wolves have brought a new unease to the Blackroot Vale in the wake of the War of the Ring."; 
